'''''Somewhere in Africa: The Cries of humanity''''' ni film y'ikinamico yo muri [[Gana]]  ya 2011 iyobowe na Frank Rajah Arase, yakinwe na Majid Michel, Martha Ankomah na Kofi Adjorlolo. Yakiriye kandidatire 7 mu bihembo bya 9 bya Afurika Movie Academy Awards harimo ibyiciro: Umukinnyi witwaye neza mu nshingano zambere, Ibyagezweho mu majwi, Ibyagezweho mu ngaruka ziboneka no kugerwaho na Make-Up. Majid Michel niwe wahawe igihembo cyonyine cya film.

